<p />
<h4><a name="Yum_Deployment"></a> * Yum Deployment </h4>
<p /> <ol>
<li> Install new mash script(s)
</li> <li> <s>Run the script that creates and populates the new directories</s> Run script to update .mash files
</li> <li> Run mash update script itself
</li> <li> Verify the new contents — same number of packages per dir? same sizes? what?
</li> <li> Run the script that changes the <code>3.0</code> structures
</li> <li> Verify symlinks (via making fermicloud machines and doing test installs from 'osg-release-itb')
</li></ol> 
<p /> <ul>
<li> <a href="https://twiki.opensciencegrid.org/twiki/pub/SoftwareTeam/SP021_NewVersionsDetails/oct1-repo-itb-deployment-plan.txt" target="_top">oct1-repo-itb-deployment-plan.txt</a>: script-like deployment plan for repo-itb on oct1
</li></ul> 
<p />
<h3><a name="Routine_Deployment_of_New_Series"></a> Routine Deployment of New Series </h3>
<p />
<h4><a name="1_Subversion"></a> 1  Subversion </h4>
<p />
The current existing release series is called OLD (e.g., 3.1) and the new release series is called NEW (e.g., 3.2).
<p /> <ol>
<li> Notify users to stop committing until further notice
</li> <li> Copy <code>trunk</code> to <code>branches/osg-<em>OLD</em></code>
</li> <li> Merge changes from <code>branches/upcoming</code> to <code>trunk</code>, as desired
</li> <li> Copy <code>trunk</code> to <code>tags/osg-<em>NEW</em>-start</code>
</li> <li> Copy <code>branches/upcoming</code> to <code>tags/upcoming-to-<em>NEW</em></code>
</li> <li> Delete from <code>branches/upcoming</code> everything that was merged above
</li> <li> Delete from <code>trunk</code> everything that is no longer needed with commit messages explaining why
</li> <li> Notify users that changes are done
</li></ol> 
<p />
<h4><a name="2_Koji"></a> 2  Koji </h4>
<p /> <ol>
<li> Add tags: <code>osg-<em>N</em>.<em>M</em>-el*-build</code>, <code>osg-<em>N</em>.<em>M</em>-el*-{development,testing,prerelease,release,contrib}</code>
</li> <li> Add build targets: <code>osg-<em>N</em>.<em>M</em>-el*</code> &rarr; (<code>osg-<em>N</em>.<em>M</em>-el*-build</code>, <code>osg-<em>N</em>.<em>M</em>-el*-development</code>)
</li> <li> Change existing build targets: <code>osg-el*</code> &rarr; (<code>osg-<em>N</em>.<em>M</em>-el*-build</code>, <code>osg-<em>N</em>.<em>M</em>-el*-development</code>)
</li> <li> Change inheritance of <code>osg-el*-upcoming-build</code>: inherit from <code>osg-<em>N</em>.<em>M</em>-el*-build</code> instead of the previous series
</li></ol> 
<p />
<h4><a name="3_Yum"></a> 3  Yum </h4> <ol>
<li> Run mash script to create new version directory and populate it (details to come later)
</li></ol> </div><!-- /patternTopic-->
